{"tid":614401,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入嚟分享下夾band問題","createTime":"2018-04-02T13:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T13:56:40.000Z","uid":179951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1118e1560b60112607560940dbc7ad2f69a315cd","tid":614401,"uid":179951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"我係一個鼓手<br />\n之前跟咗老師學一段時間, 可以話係學咗個基本，然後基本都係自學<br />\n自己有一隊band， 係band友眼中我係一個打鼓唔差嘅人，大部分想夾嘅歌我都打到。 但係其實我有一個小秘密~就係睇譜好差 。。 其實我本身就想表演， 但係其實表演係咪一定要睇譜? 定係只要打到個感覺就可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad3c47e1453296a2a60fd3d49c1a9625e26dd00","tid":614401,"uid":23275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"覺得鼓唔似其他樂器一定要跟足<br />\n只要唔係錯拍子 夾band唔睇譜冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n如果做session就另計啦 人地可能要你每一粒都要準"},{"pid":"6fac5bf7e1427eb593e96c29533800603fe93aab","tid":614401,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"鼓 自己改譜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c16ec91f7cb14c3a86f164c5f823697b71faca7","tid":614401,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"好多polygon友<br />\n<br />\n唔練野<br />\n<br />\n琴同結他一齊撞<br />\n<br />\n飛機友<br />\n<br />\n潛水友"},{"pid":"8d48c7fa2df24ce7c5822a632009109fa0840c0a","tid":614401,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"想玩既野比較冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6eedf5a16d4adb6c4ca85a458c6a40c4f2b5cc","tid":614401,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"夾band 應該需要有自己style <br />\n<br />\n換言之, 無論cover / 自己歌都好應該都需要經過消化 / 思考過先, 咁就唔應該存在咩要睇譜打既問題<br />\n再唔係背左份譜佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw表演果時唔係應該背左份譜ga咩, 就算有譜都只係少少提醒作用啫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5bf3113e18f0a115f7f546b58303f6a160fc3a","tid":614401,"uid":111604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1118e1560b60112607560940dbc7ad2f69a315cd","tid":614401,"uid":179951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"我係一個鼓手<br />\n之前跟咗老師學一段時間, 可以話係學咗個基本，然後基本都係自學<br />\n自己有一隊band， 係band友眼中我係一個打鼓唔差嘅人，大部分想夾嘅歌我都打到。 但係其實我有一個小秘密~就係睇譜好差 。。 其實我本身就想表演， 但係其實表演係咪一定要睇譜? 定係只要打到個感覺就可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"如果你只係玩4 5首歌, 唔駛睇譜可以玩得返出黎係基本<br />\n你玩到一場20幾30首歌, 要部ipad放少少notes上台我覺得無問題<br />\n其他好似上面巴打講差唔多<br />\n唔係演唱會級數, 唔會要你每一粒音都準<br />\n當然唔代表要對自己無要求"},{"pid":"a27c33c0642fad3efb27702ed3bdcc26aa6f75da","tid":614401,"uid":111604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec6eedf5a16d4adb6c4ca85a458c6a40c4f2b5cc","tid":614401,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"夾band 應該需要有自己style <br />\n<br />\n換言之, 無論cover / 自己歌都好應該都需要經過消化 / 思考過先, 咁就唔應該存在咩要睇譜打既問題<br />\n再唔係背左份譜佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw表演果時唔係應該背左份譜ga咩, 就算有譜都只係少少提醒作用啫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"所以我每次都同學生講<br />\n如果你係一個觀眾<br />\n見到個樂手喺台上每秒鐘都係望住份譜彈唔望你地<br />\n個感覺係點<br />\n如果你睇演唱會, 陳奕迅剩係望住歌詞你又會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4960c6c658c35c6dedd6c1f88b70c5c5ee93483a","tid":614401,"uid":18786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d48c7fa2df24ce7c5822a6320091